blog.description: You can call me Ash. Thirty one and still growing up now. This blog is about loving Taylor and loving you all. I will reach out to you. I got a full palm high five off Taylor and I’m absolutely taking that. I never get no notes on nuffin except this one time when Tay liked my post and my broken bones mended. I live in permanent countdown to the times I get to spend with @ekswiftie. I live blog Taylor events at #ash live. @islandbreezeee made my banner.

summary:
New Orleans Swifties- I Need You! 
I need Swiftie assistance! My fiancé Sal thinks we are camping here in the UK for our...
body:
New Orleans Swifties- I Need You!

I need Swiftie assistance! My fiancé Sal thinks we are camping here in the UK for our holidays in September, but actually I’ve booked flights and tickets for Rep Tour NOLA! I want to reveal the surprise on the way to the airport using a video packed full of Swifties saying, “Welcome to NOLA!” or, “NOLA’s waiting for you!”, singing a couple lines, or whatever else you felt like, wearing tour outfits, merch, flashing tickets, whatever! Swiftie creativity is welcome if you have better ideas. I’ll need all videos by August 17th so I can edit together. Please send videos to welcometonolaproject@gmail.com

I would appreciate it SO MUCH if you share this far and wide. Of course I’ll be trying to get Tay to see it too, and thank everyone involved. If you’d like to send the video by another means, just let me know. Non-NOLA Swifties you’re welcome too!

Sal works on curing cancer as her day job so she deserves this holiday so much. Check out #Tales of Sal on my blog if you want to see how dedicated to Taylor she is. Any help so gratefully received. Love you all ♥️
